    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/2868a29b76ac0fe28cc57a3e1bae5c26.poster.avif?t=1724429892\" width=612 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/2868a29b76ac0fe28cc57a3e1bae5c26.webm?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/2868a29b76ac0fe28cc57a3e1bae5c26.mp4?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Warmage: Prologue is a free version of Warmage. Discover and explore the universe and core gameplay of this tactical roguelite and get a preview of the experience that awaits you in the full game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/96e1320da61548096770b223767e2dbd.poster.avif?t=1724429892\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/96e1320da61548096770b223767e2dbd.webm?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/96e1320da61548096770b223767e2dbd.mp4?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>Warmage: Prologue</strong> is a <strong>roguelite grid-based turn-based tactical combat</strong> game where you play as a young warmage tasked with defending his city against an unknown evil.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as 3 different archetypes with unique gameplay<br></li><li>Varied and refreshing tactical combat<br></li><li>After each battle, power up your warmage and buy various attacks and items<br></li><li>Choose your next mission on the city map carefully<br></li><li>Differents objectives for each battle<br></li><li>Over 45 spells and 38 items to combine to create the ultimate warmage</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/ac25f0f14fe9b175b939e98cd3a32c07.avif?t=1724429892\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight</strong></h2>Use a wide variety of weapons and spells to defeat waves of ennemies in a turn by turn combat. Various ennemies will challenge you in different ways, think carefully about each movement and each attack as a single error can put you in perilous situations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/e09651900b0855e58f524bb79b485f88.avif?t=1724429892\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade</strong></h2>Use the gems collected during the fights to buy new spells, upgrade the ones you already have and buy new items. With each level gained, you can upgrade one of you primary caracteristic which will improve the power of your attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/64d33a164097fff065b6ee22abac4a7c.avif?t=1724429892\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Burn them all</strong></h2>Now that you have a deadly warmage with powerfull spells, defeat all whom will stand in your way !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/457a9c906a1b41128abd67e8cf083b05.poster.avif?t=1724429892\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/457a9c906a1b41128abd67e8cf083b05.webm?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/457a9c906a1b41128abd67e8cf083b05.mp4?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use your environment</strong></h2>The surroundings aren't just for show, they can be your greatest ally in escaping deadly situations. Learn to harness them to your advantage !<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/86144dfded54516171bde065965a71d6.poster.avif?t=1724429892\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/86144dfded54516171bde065965a71d6.webm?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/86144dfded54516171bde065965a71d6.mp4?t=1724429892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Defend your city</strong></h2>Your city is attacked by an unkown evil. You have to help the citizens, others warmages and important people to survive!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097450/extras/18dc437fcb01ffb71aa071bbc8d5f0bc.avif?t=1724429892\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
